 <title>We&#039;re Going to the Zoo</title>
 <link>http://vse.la/kids-songs/were-going-zoo</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#039;re going to the zoo, &lt;br /&gt;
To see a kangaroo,&lt;br /&gt;
And a lion too,&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;re going to the zoo. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The monkeys swing and climb,&lt;br /&gt;
They know it&#039;s feeding time,&lt;br /&gt;
The polar bears and seals, &lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy their fishy meals.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&#039;re going to the zoo, &lt;br /&gt;
To see a kangaroo,&lt;br /&gt;
And a lion too,&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;re going to the zoo. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The snakes all slide along, &lt;br /&gt;
The skunk just makes a pong, &lt;br /&gt;
The tiger gives a roar,&lt;br /&gt;
He wants to eat some more. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&#039;re going to the zoo, &lt;br /&gt;
To see a kangaroo,&lt;br /&gt;
And a lion too,&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;re going to the zoo. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The penguin needs to hide, &lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s much too hot outside, &lt;br /&gt;
But the lizard&#039;s having fun, &lt;br /&gt;
Lying in the sun!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&#039;re going to the zoo, &lt;br /&gt;
To see a kangaroo,&lt;br /&gt;
And a lion too,&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;re going to the zoo. &lt;br /&gt;
 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
